  <body>
    <h1>Nested List Test Page</h1>
    <p>
      This page tests nested ordered and unordered lists. Each nested list should appear indented
      under its parent item. <a href="/">Back to main demo</a>
    </p>
    <hr />
    <h2>Expected Structure:</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Simple ordered list: 1, 2, (2.1, 2.2 nested), 3</li>
      <li>Simple unordered list: same structure with bullets</li>
      <li>Complex ordered list: multiple levels of nesting (2.1.2, 3.2.1, etc.)</li>
      <li>Mixed list: ordered with unordered sublists (install options, usage tips)</li>
    </ul>
    <hr />
    <h2>Rendered Output:</h2>
    <RichTextLexical nodes={nestedListTestContent.root.children} />
  </body>
</html>
